   pollination; deceit; extrafloral nectaries; Aspidosperma
   quebracho-blanco},
Keywords-Plus = {POLLEN-OVULE RATIOS; BREEDING SYSTEMS; PLANTS; ORCHIDACEAE; NECTARIES;
