   Shuttleworth, Adam; Johnson, Steven D.; Juergens, Andreas, Univ KwaZulu Natal, Sch Life Sci, Private Bag X01, ZA-3209 Pietermaritzburg, South Africa.
   Juergens, Andreas, Tech Univ Darmstadt, Dept Biol, Plant Chem Ecol, Schnittspahnstr 10, D-64287 Darmstadt, Germany.},
